These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, nectarine, cucumber, corn
There are 4 different nationalities: american, polish, malaysian, australian
1. the polish is on the left of the american##1
2. the person eating lemon is the australian##1
3. the malaysian is on the right of the american##1
4. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the australian##1
5. the person eating corn is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | corn | cucumber | nectarine | lemon   |
| Nationality   | polish  | american     | malaysian   | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, magic-tricks, collecting, traveling
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, rowing, water-polo
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | collecting | traveling | magic-tricks | rock-climbing    |
| Sport   | rowing    | cricket      | biathlon | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, reading, drawing, hiking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, satire, comedy, martial-arts
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | dancing | hiking | drawing   | reading |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | comedy | martial-arts | satire         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, time-travel, crime, animation
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, badminton, swimming, rowing
1. the person who's sport is badminton is the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | time-travel | fantasy  | crime      |
| Sport         | badminton | rowing   | swimming | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, apple, mango, grapes
4 different pets are kept: ferret, bird, goldfish, frog
1. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the person eating grapes is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | grapes | mango | apple | asparagus |
| Pet    | ferret       | frog | goldfish | bird     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, turkish, german, argentine
4 different pets are kept: dog, bird, hedgehog, pony
1. the turkish is on the far right##1
2. the argentine is on the left of the german##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the german##1
5. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | argentine | german | egyptian | turkish |
| Pet           | dog      | hedgehog | pony | bird    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, metal, pop, folk
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, bird, hedgehog
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | pop | metal | reggae | folk  |
| Pet           | bird | cat | hedgehog       | dog |

