.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, software-developer, social-worker, dancer
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, snowmobile, roller, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the software-developer##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is the dancer##1
3. the software-developer is on the right of the police-officer##1
4. the social-worker is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the train is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | social-worker | police-officer      | software-developer | dancer |
| Transport   | train          | snowmobile | roller     | helicopter    |

