.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, sports, animation, martial-arts
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike, snowmobile, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports    | animation       | crime | martial-arts   |
| Transport     | quad-bike | snowmobile | boat   | scooter |

