.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, water, soy-milk, 7up
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, ship, snowmobile, van
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | tea | soy-milk  | water | 7up |
| Transport   | van | snowmobile | ship          | boat    |

