2. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of techno##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking 7up is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | 7up  | juice | mirinda |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | techno | electronic           | soul   |

