3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk  | mirinda | almond-milk   |
| Pet        | turtle | goldfish | chinchilla    | horse |

