.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving, hiking, fishing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, crime, western, fantasy
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
3. the person watching western movies is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | hiking | fishing | filmmaking |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy     | western    | romance      | crime   |

