.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, colombian, dutch, turkish
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, van, subway, quad-bike
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the colombian##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the turkish##1
3. the german is on the left of the dutch##1
4. the turkish is the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the bus is on the left of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | german | dutch | colombian | turkish   |
| Transport     | subway  | bus    | van       | quad-bike |

 